text: Engina australis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pisaniidae. ==Description== ==Distribution== This species occurs in the Indian Ocean off the Aldabra Atoll. ==References== * Taylor, J.D. (1973). Provisional list of the mollusca of Aldabra Atoll. ==External links== * Category:Pisaniidae Category:Gastropods described in 1871
title: Engina australis
